                <div class="tit_nav">
                    <span class="tit_l">您所在位置：</span><a href="/Home/Index">首页</a><b>></b><span>案例信息</span>
                </div>
                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6600" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">TEC-0102</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9801 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">盾构机从跟跑到领跑：铁建重工的技术赶超矛盾与破解</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Shield machine from following to leading: the contradiction and solution of the technical catch-up of CRCHI</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">曾德麟，欧阳桃花，崔宏超，龚克，倪泽波，蔡家玮</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">北京交通大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中国铁建重工集团股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">机械、电机工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">研发部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">14 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">技术赶超；冷启动；产品迭代与技术升级；后发企业；卡脖子技术；2022百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Technology catch-up; Cold start; Product iteration and technology upgrading; Latecomer; Neck-jamming technology</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">盾构机作为现代化隧道工程施工中的核心装备，被誉为“皇冠上的明珠”。因其技术复杂、行业壁垒高，国内盾构机产业曾长期被国际企业垄断。为突破技术封锁，实现技术自立，诸多企业不断探索。经实践检验，以“合资、收购”的方式无法引进核心技术且企业后劲不足。而成立于2006年的铁建重工则坚持在学习中追赶、在追赶中超越，不断破解技术赶超矛盾，实现了“国之重器”盾构机从跟跑到领跑的跃迁，探索出了一套“中国盾构技术赶超模式”。目前，国产盾构机不仅满足了国内市场需求，还占领了2/3的全球市场。本文以铁建重工为案例对象，讲述了大国技术竞争日趋激烈的背景下，其如何逐步破解“冷启动”、“老产品迭代创新与新产品技术升级”技术赶超矛盾的故事。本案例可以引导学生深度探讨中国后发企业突破“卡脖子技术”的经验启示，学习后发企业技术赶超相关知识，对学生进行价值观引领，培养爱国情怀，将个人追求融入中华民族复兴的中国梦。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">As the core equipment in the construction of modern tunnel engineering, shield machine is known as the &quot;pearl on the crown&quot;. Because of complex technology and high industrial barriers, domestic shield machine industry has been monopolized by international enterprises for a long time. In order to break through the technological blockade and realize technological independence, many enterprises continue to explore. It has proved that the core technology cannot be introduced by means of &quot;joint venture and acquisition&quot; in practice, and the enterprise doesn&#39;t have sufficient stamina. However, CRCHI, which is founded in 2006, sticks to catching up in learning, and surpassing in catching up. Besides, this company constantly solves the contradiction of technology catch-up. Finally, it has realized the technological leap of shield machine and explored a set of The Catch-up Mode of Chinese Shield Model. At present, the domestic shield machine not only meets the demand of domestic market, but also occupies two thirds of the global market. Taking CRCHI as the case object, this case tells the story of how to solve the contradiction of &quot;cold start&quot; and &quot;iterative innovation of old products and technology upgrading of new product&quot; under the background of increasingly fierce technology competition. This case can guide students to deeply explore the experience and enlightenment of China&#39;s latecomer enterprises to break through the &quot;neck-jamming technology&quot;, learn the relevant knowledge of technological catch-up of enterprises, and help to guide the students&#39; values, cultivate patriotism, and integrate their personal pursuit into the Chinese dream of national rejuvenation.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《技术创新管理》、《创新管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">后发企业技术赶超概念；技术跟随战略与冷启动概念；技术领先战略、产品迭代与技术升级概念；技术赶超模式——双循环创新组织模型；“卡脖子技术”概念</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-09</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
